## Test Folder Purity (MANDATORY)

`playwright/tests/` must contain **only `.spec.ts` files**. Shared helpers go in `playwright/src/utils/`, `playwright/src/data-models/`, or `playwright/src/data-factories/`. Never create `.ts` helper files alongside spec files.

